            "scope": "Project Console queue and disclosure conventions; GitHub <code>Development level<\/code> and workflow <code>Status<\/code>; delegated-foundation authority; Change Audit metadata; reader navigation and terminology; area and issue ownership; legislative drafting form; external-source versus internal-work provenance; Horizon and area source-development descriptions; public-intake security; GitHub and publication readback; deterministic Integrity coverage; and full validation.",
            "effect": "No Proposal Quality Score, scoring rubric, threshold, score band, Review Ready determination, rebaseline, or <strong>Runs<\/strong> count changed. Lifecycle and workflow fields were synchronized only to their already established canonical meanings."
